# 🛍️ Product Review Sentiment Analyzer

## 📌 About
NLP model that classifies Amazon product reviews 
as Positive or Negative using Machine Learning.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python
- Scikit-learn
- TF-IDF Vectorization
- Logistic Regression
- Google Colab

## 📊 Results
- Accuracy: 90%+
- Dataset: Amazon Product Reviews
- Classes: Positive / Negative

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Open ml.ipynb in Google Colab
2. Run all cells in order
3. Enter your review in last cell
4. Get Positive/Negative prediction!

